**Typography Rules:**
- **Body text:** 16-18px, 1.6-1.75 line height
- **Headings:** Tighter line height (1.2-1.4)
- **Max line length:** 65-75 characters
- **Weight:** Regular (400) for body, Medium (500) or Semibold (600) for emphasis

