## 5. Imagery Guidelines

### 5.1 Photography Style

**Characteristics:**
- Natural lighting preferred
- Authentic moments, not staged
- Clean compositions
- Muted, sophisticated color grading

**Avoid:**
- Stock photography clichés
- Overly filtered images
- Cluttered compositions
- Artificial-looking setups

### 5.2 Illustrations & Graphics

**Style:**
- Clean, minimal line work
- Geometric where appropriate
- Functional, not decorative
- Consistent stroke weights

**Avoid:**
- Overly playful or cartoonish styles
- Complex illustrations that distract
- Trendy styles that will date quickly

### 5.3 Icons

**Guidelines:**
- Consistent stroke width (1.5-2px)
- Rounded line caps
- Clear at small sizes
- Match overall design language

**Recommended Sets:**
- Lucide Icons
- Heroicons
- Feather Icons

