## 7. Responsive Design

### 7.1 Breakpoints

```css
/* Mobile first */
--ns-bp-sm: 640px;   /* Small screens */
--ns-bp-md: 768px;   /* Tablets */
--ns-bp-lg: 1024px;  /* Laptops */
--ns-bp-xl: 1280px;  /* Desktops */
--ns-bp-2xl: 1536px; /* Large screens */
```

### 7.2 Mobile Guidelines

- Touch targets: 44px minimum
- Readable text without zooming (16px minimum)
- Single column layouts where appropriate
- Thumb-friendly navigation placement

### 7.3 Desktop Guidelines

- Max content width: 1200px (prose: 65-75ch)
- Utilize space without feeling empty
- Consider multi-column layouts
- Maintain visual hierarchy at larger sizes

