## 9. Brand Don'ts

### 9.1 Visual Don'ts

❌ Gradients (unless very subtle)
❌ Multiple fonts in one composition
❌ Busy backgrounds
❌ Stock photography clichés
❌ Rainbow/excessive color variation
❌ Decorative elements without purpose

### 9.2 Communication Don'ts

❌ Hype language ("Amazing!", "Game-changer!")
❌ Pressure tactics ("Limited time!", "Don't miss out!")
❌ Empty superlatives ("Best", "Ultimate", "Perfect")
❌ Corporate jargon ("Leverage", "Synergy", "Disrupt")

### 9.3 Positioning Don'ts

❌ Comparing to competitors negatively
❌ Making promises we can't keep
❌ Overstating capabilities
❌ Appealing to status or envy

